'''香港快閃板球賽'''是一項在2016年首次舉辦的香港職業板球比賽，第一屆有4隊參賽<ref>[http://hkcricket.org/en/news/Hong-Kong-T20-Blitz-teams-revealed/559/ Hong Kong T20 Blitz teams revealed]</ref><ref>[http://hkcricket.org/en/news/Franchises-up-for-sale-in-new-Hong-Kong-T20-Blitz-League/538/  Franchises up for sale in new Hong Kong T20 Blitz League]</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://hkcricket.org/en/news/CEO-Tim-Cutler-reveals-impact-of-WT20/531/ |title=Tim Cutler reveals impact of WT20 |access-date=2020-12-27 |archive-date=2016-05-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160506202229/http://hkcricket.org/en/news/CEO-Tim-Cutler-reveals-impact-of-WT20/531/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>[http://hkcricket.org/en/news/Hong-Kong-exit-ICC-World-Twenty20-with-future-in-mind/526/ Hong Kong exit ICC World Twenty20 with future in mind]</ref><ref>[Clarke signs up for Hong Kong's domestic T20 league]</ref>，決賽因為天雨關係取消，由蛀木蟲島勇士和九龍廣東人共享冠軍榮譽。2019年7月，這項賽事因為財政問題而取消<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.emergingcricket.com/news/hong-kong-t20-blitz-cancelled-sixes-under-threat/ |title=BREAKING: Hong Kong T20 Blitz to be axed, Sixes also under threat |work=Emerging Cricket |accessdate=22 July 2019 |archive-date=2020-11-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201126105303/https://emergingcricket.com/news/hong-kong-t20-blitz-cancelled-sixes-under-threat/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==歷史==
香港板球總會在2016年4月宣佈會舉辦一項板球比賽，以助香港和周邊國家發展板球運動。比賽以[[2020_(板球)|2020]]規則進行，由DTC電信贊助<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://hkcricket.org/en/news/DTC-Mobile-sign-as-title-sponsors-for-Hong-Kong-T20-Blitz/567/ |title=DTC Mobile sign as title sponsors for Hong Kong T20 Blitz |access-date=2020-12-27 |archive-date=2016-09-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160925223322/http://hkcricket.org/en/news/DTC-Mobile-sign-as-title-sponsors-for-Hong-Kong-T20-Blitz/567/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.scmp.com/sport/other-sport/article/1935977/hong-kong-t20-blitz-expected-attract-overseas-cricket-talent |title=Hong Kong T20 Blitz expected to attract overseas cricket talent |access-date=2020-12-27 |archive-date=2020-11-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109085030/https://www.scmp.com/sport/other-sport/article/1935977/hong-kong-t20-blitz-expected-attract-overseas-cricket-talent |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="#1">{{Cite web |url=http://www.scmp.com/sport/hong-kong/article/1939389/two-players-will-miss-out-draft-hong-kongs-first-twenty20-blitz |title=Two players will miss out on draft for Hong Kong’s first Twenty20 Blitz tournament |access-date=2020-12-27 |archive-date=2019-02-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190222204728/https://www.scmp.com/sport/hong-kong/article/1939389/two-players-will-miss-out-draft-hong-kongs-first-twenty20-blitz |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>[http://hkcricket.org/en/news/Final-call-on-Bids-for-Hong-Kong-T20-Blitz/551/ Final call on Bids for Hong Kong T20 Blitz]</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://hkcricket.org/en/news/Hong-Kong-Mens-team-receive-major-funding-boost-from-HKSI-af/548/ |title=Hong Kong Men's team receive major funding boost from HKSI after World T20 campaign |access-date=2020-12-27 |archive-date=2016-04-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160415233350/http://www.hkcricket.org/en/news/Hong-Kong-Mens-team-receive-major-funding-boost-from-HKSI-af/548/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://hkcricket.org/en/news/Hong-Kong-T20-Blitz-franchise-bidding-opens/547/ |title=Hong Kong T20 Blitz franchise bidding opens! |access-date=2020-12-27 |archive-date=2016-04-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160415232942/http://www.hkcricket.org/en/news/Hong-Kong-T20-Blitz-franchise-bidding-opens/547/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，賽事獎金為20萬港元。第一屆有4隊參賽，本土球員由抽籤形式分配，而各球隊亦大量簽下外藉球員<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.scmp.com/sport/article/1936925/three-hong-kong-t20-blitz-franchises-taken-one-more-still-grabs |title=Three Hong Kong T20 Blitz franchises taken, one more still up for grabs |access-date=2020-12-27 |archive-date=2020-11-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108184232/http://www.scmp.com/sport/article/1936925/three-hong-kong-t20-blitz-franchises-taken-one-more-still-grabs |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>[http://hkcricket.org/en/news/Woodworm-take-over-Island-Warriors/583/  Woodworm take over Island Warriors]</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.scmp.com/sport/article/1943088/kowloon-cantons-women-hope-spark-hong-kong-cricket-revolution-t20-blitz |title=Kowloon Cantons women hope to spark Hong Kong cricket revolution at T20 Blitz |access-date=2020-12-27 |archive-date=2018-06-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180615135005/http://www.scmp.com/sport/article/1943088/kowloon-cantons-women-hope-spark-hong-kong-cricket-revolution-t20-blitz |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[香港板球男子代表隊|香港板球男子代表隊]]隊長[[坦维尔·阿夫扎尔|坦维尔·阿夫扎尔]]被抽至蛀木蟲島勇士<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.scmp.com/sport/article/1939549/tanwir-afzal-babar-hayat-are-first-two-picks-hong-kong-t20-blitz-dtc-named |title=Tanwir Afzal, Babar Hayat are first two picks for Hong Kong T20 Blitz – DTC named title sponsor |access-date=2020-12-27 |archive-date=2020-11-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108124557/http://www.scmp.com/sport/article/1939549/tanwir-afzal-babar-hayat-are-first-two-picks-hong-kong-t20-blitz-dtc-named |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.scmp.com/sport/other-sport/article/1944650/hong-kong-t20-blitz-feature-top-talent-australia-and-india-teams |title=Hong Kong T20 Blitz to feature top talent from Australia and India as teams release provisional squads |access-date=2020-12-27 |archive-date=2020-11-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108112759/http://www.scmp.com/sport/other-sport/article/1944650/hong-kong-t20-blitz-feature-top-talent-australia-and-india-teams |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>[http://hkcricket.org/en/news/HKCA-to-welcome-Michael-Clarke-for-DTC-Hong-Kong-T20-Blitz/584/ HKCA to welcome Michael Clarke for DTC Hong Kong T20 Blitz]</ref><ref name="#1"/> 。蛀木蟲島勇士在2017年改名為港島聯，以外亦加入第五隊城市啟德<ref>[http://m.scmp.com/sport/hong-kong/article/2009420/raising-stakes-hong-kong-t20-blitz-adds-fifth-franchise Raising the stakes: Hong Kong T20 Blitz adds fifth franchise]</ref>，而五隊各有一名本土球員，縱使他們沒有獲得任何重要職務。

